{
  "stem": "3690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky because I could-- I was always an organizer, so I could steal a board and sleep on a piece of board and put an old blanket on the board, and I could a little relax more.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some boys and girls weren't that active or very organized.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they didn't-- they were always afraid whatever they going to do, it's going to be bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, don't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what worse can happen to you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you need a piece of board, take it and sleep on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and I tried to help them out always, you know, to get them organized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And sometimes I even went out and got it for those people, but it was quite bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was working there for about three months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got so sick and tired of that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to take much rest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We kept working all day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had foremans used to go out and watch over us, that we don't fool around on the job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all Hungarian Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called themselves [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to wear a, a cross, like a special cross with a special uniform on it because they were in charge.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not plain Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were, they were almost even worse than the Germans, because they gave them authority, and they, they wanted to show off with their authority.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you didn't do your job, they even hit you real hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they punished you with all kind, different things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sometimes if you, if they, if they found it that you didn't do your job right, you didn't get your food.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
